quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Ṭaa, Sɩɩn, Miim."
  26,2,"Ad woto yaa Gafã Aaya-rãmba sẽn vẽnegdã."
  26,3,"Tõe tɩ fo weoogda f sũurã, b sẽn ka kõt sɩd yĩnga."
  26,4,"Tõnd sã n tʋlla, D sikda saagẽ wã yel-soalem tɩ b yubli wã kell n sulg ne-a n gεt-ɑ tɩ yɑɑ vẽenegɑ."
  26,5,"Tẽeg-paall ka wat bãmbã n yi Yolsg Naab nengẽ, rẽndame tɩ b gũda b zãn-kuidsi."
  26,6,"Ad bãmbã yagsame, la b sẽn da sãbsdã kɩbay na n wa-b lame."
  26,7,"Rẽ yĩngã bãmb pa yã tẽn-gãngã, sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn buls ɑ zugu bõn-bundɩ toor-toore sẽn yaa wagle."
  26,8,"Ad tagmas be woto pʋga, la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,9,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,10,"La (tẽeg) wakat ning fo Soabã sẽn wa n bool a Musa n yeel-ɑ: ""kẽng neb nins sẽn wẽg b mensã nengẽ""."
  26,11,"A Fɩr-aoon nebã nengẽ, n tɩ yeel-ba: "" rẽ yĩnga y pa nɑ n zoe Wẽnde?"""
  26,12,"A Muusɑ yeelɑme m Soaba! Ad mam yεεsdame tɩ b na n wa yags maam."
  26,13,"Tɩ mam yãoogã wa weooge, tɩ mam zɩlemd pa tõe gom ye, bɩ F tʋms a Haarʋʋn n lagem maam."
  26,14,"La mam rag n beeg-b lame, tɩ m yaεεsd tɩ b na n wa kʋ maam."
  26,15,"Tɩ [Wẽnd] yeele: "" rẽ kõ n yɩ ye! Kẽng-y yãmb y yiibã, ad Tõnd bee ne yãmb n kelgdẽ."
  26,16,"Kẽng-y yãmb y yiibã a Fɩr-ʿaoon nengẽ n tɩ yeel-a: ""ad tõnd yaa bõn-naandsã Gʋʋndã Tẽn-tʋʋmba''."
  26,17,"Tɩ fo bas ɭsraεεl koambã tɩ tũ tõndo""."
  26,18,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeel yã: ''rẽ yĩnga tõnd pa wub foom tõnd nengẽ tɩ fo yaa bi-kɩdga? Tɩ fo zĩnd tõnd nengẽ yʋʋma?''"
  26,19,"Tɩ fo tʋm tʋʋm ning fo sẽn tʋmã, tɩ fo yaa sõm-zɩta""."
  26,20,"La a Musa yeel yã: ""mam tʋm-a-la wakat-kãngã tɩ mam yaa menemda.''"
  26,21,"Mam zoeeme n yi yãmba, mam sẽn wa n yaeesdã: rẽ poorẽ tɩ mam Soabã kõ maam Bʋʋd minim la A maan tɩ mam naag Tẽn-tʋʋmbã pʋgẽ."
  26,22,"Lɑ fo sẽn gʋʋl mɑɑmɑ yaa neema fo sẽn tɑr-ɑ n tãɑsd maam, tɩ fo yaool n kɩtame t'a ɭsraεεl koambã yaa fo yembse lɑ f bɑs mɑɑm. (lɑ rẽ pɑ gɩdgd mɑɑm tɩ m dɑ bool foo ye)."
  26,23,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeel yã: "" yaa bõe la bõn-naandsã Soaba?"""
  26,24,"La a Musa yeele: "" yɑɑ saas la tẽng la bũmb nins sẽn be b yiibã sʋk Soabã, tɩ yãmb sã n yɩɩme n yaa bãng-n-wãag-rãmba""."
  26,25,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeel neb nins sẽn be yẽ kɩrenga: ""y wʋmdame bɩ?"""
  26,26,"""Ta a Muusa yeele: ""A yaa yãmb Soabã la yãmb bɑ-rãmb sẽn deng tɑoorã Soabɑ""."
  26,27,"Ta a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeele: ""ad y Tẽn-tʋʋm ning b sẽn tʋms tɩ wa yãmb nengẽ wã yaa gãeenga""."
  26,28,"T'a a Musa yeele: ""A yaa wĩntoog sẽn pukdẽ la a sẽn lʋɩtẽ lɑ bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã Soaba, tɩ yãmb sã n tara yam n tagsd n getẽ""."
  26,29,"La a Fɩr-ʿaoon yeel yã: ""la tɩ fo sã n tũ soab zẽng sẽn ka maam, m na pag-f bãense""."
  26,30,"T'a a Musa yeele:"" bɑ tɩ mam sã n wa ne bũmb sẽn sɩdgd-m tɩ yɑɑ vẽenegɑ?"""
  26,31,"Ta a [Fɩr-ʿaoon] yeele: "" bɩ f wa ne-a tɩ sã n mikame tɩ fo yaa sɩd-soaba""."
  26,32,"T'a [Musa] lobg a rasaarã t'a lebg waaf tɩ yɑɑ vẽenega."
  26,33,"La a rɩk a nugã n tʋm a bãokẽ wã, tɩ nugã lebg pεεlg tɩ b neẽ."
  26,34,"La a [Fɩr-ʿaoon] yeel kug-zĩidb nins sẽn be yẽ kɩrengã: ""ad yãoã yaa tɩ-mita,"
  26,35,"n rat n yiis yãmb y tẽngẽ wã ne a tɩɩmã, la yãmb sagenda maam ne bõe?"""
  26,36,"La b yeele: ""kɩt tɩ yẽ la a ma-biigã lebg n kuli, la f tʋms tẽngã pʋgẽ tɩ b tigim,"
  26,37,"n wa ne tɩ-mit fãa fo nengẽ""."
  26,38,"Tɩ tɩtã-rãmb na n tigim taab raar ning b sẽn yãkã."
  26,39,"La b na n yeel nebã: ""rẽ yĩngã yãmb tigim n sεεme?,"
  26,40,"Tõe tɩ tõnd tũ tɩtã-rãmbã tɩ b sã n wili"""
  26,41,"La tɩtã-rãmb sẽn wa n wa wã, b yeela a Fɩr-ʿaoona: ""rẽ yĩngã tõnd tara keoor tɩ tõnd sã n wili?"""
  26,42,"La a yeel yã: ""n-yẽe, yãmb na n lebga mam pẽnegdba!"
  26,43,"La a Musa yeel-ba: ""lob-y bũmb nins yãmb sẽn na n lobã""."
  26,44,"La b lob b wĩyã la rasapã n yeele: ""ne a Fɩr-ʿaoon zɩslemã, yaa tõnd n na n wili""."
  26,45,"La a Musa lobg a rasaarã t'a na n vel bãmb sẽn maanã."
  26,46,"Tɩ tɩtã-rãmb lʋɩ n maan suguudu."
  26,47,"N yeele: "" D kõo sɩd ne bõn-naands Soabã,"
  26,48,"a Musa la a Harʋʋn Soabã""."
  26,49,"La a [Fɩr-ʿaoon] yeele: ""yãmb kõ-a-la sɩda taoor tɩ mam ka kõ yãmb sore? Ad yaa yẽnda la yãmb kãsmã, sẽn wĩnig yãmb tɩɩmã, yɩ bilfu y na bãnge, m na n (kɩtame tɩ b) kʋʋs y nusã la y naoã n tul taaba, n lulg-y fãa gilli""."
  26,50,"La b yeele: ""yell ka be ye! ad yaa tõnd Soabã nengẽ la tõnd lebgda''."
  26,51,"Ad tõnd tara tʋlsem ne tõnd Soabã t'A yaaf tõnd tʋʋm-tuutsã, tõnd sẽn yaa rãeenem sɩd-kõtbã."
  26,52,"La Tõnd toola wahɩ tɩ kẽng a Musa nengẽ [n yeel-a] : ""loog ne f nebã, ad b na n pʋga yãmba""."
  26,53,"T'a Fɩr-ʿaoon na n tʋms tɩ b bool tẽmsã pʋgẽ tɩ b yek taaba."
  26,54,"""Bãmbã yaa neb kɩdg bala,"
  26,55,"La ad b puuga tõnd sũyã"
  26,56,"tɩ tõnd fãa gill yaool n yaa gũus-m-mens-rãmba""."
  26,57,"Tɩ Tõnd na n yiis-b pʋtã pʋsẽ la ko-ninã pʋsẽ."
  26,58,"La arzεksẽ la waoogr zĩisẽ."
  26,59,"Yaa woto tɩ Tõnd rɩk a faadã n kõ a ɭsraεεl koambã."
  26,60,"Tɩ bãmb na n pʋg-b wĩntoog yiib wakato."
  26,61,"Wakat ning zãma a yiibã sẽn wa n yãnd taaba, a Musa nebã yeelame: ""ad b na n paama tõndo""."
  26,62,"La a yeele: ""tek-y woto, ad mam Soabã bee ne maam, A na n kãnda maam""."
  26,63,"Tɩ Tõnd na n tʋms wahɩ tɩ kẽng a Musa nengẽ: ""rɩk f rasaarã n wẽ mogrã"". T'a pãrg n maan tɩ yembr fãa lebg wala tãm-bedre."
  26,64,"Tɩ Tõnd kɩt tɩ neb a taabã [a Fɩr-ʿaoon ne a nebã] pẽnege."
  26,65,"La Tõnd tɩlg a Musa la neb nins sẽn naag yẽnda wã fãa."
  26,66,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd na n bõr neb a taaba."
  26,67,"Ad tagmas be woto pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,68,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa yolsg Naaba."
  26,69,"La karem n togs-b a ɭbraahɩɩm kɩbarã:"
  26,70,"Wakat ning a sẽn wa n yeel a saamb la a zãmã wã: ""yaa bõe la yãmb tũudã?"""
  26,71,"La b yeele: ""tõnd tũuda rʋbse n yãs ne b tũudmã lug-lugi''."
  26,72,"La a yeele: ""rẽ yĩnga b wʋmda yãmba, y sẽn wat n kot-ba?''"
  26,73,"Maa (yãmb sẽn tũud-bã) b nafda yãmbã, maa (y sã n bas n ka tũ-ba) b namsda yãmbã?"
  26,74,"La b yeele: ""ka woto ye! Tõnd mika d saam-rãmbã tɩ b maand woto""."
  26,75,"La a yeele: ""yãmb yãame, y sẽn tũud bũmb ningã wã…?"
  26,76,"Yãmb la y saam-dãmb nins sẽn reng taoorã?"
  26,77,"Ad b yaa mam bεεba, rẽnda bõn-naandsã Soabã (Wubdã)."
  26,78,"Soab ning sẽn naan maamã la A kãndg maamã;"
  26,79,"Naab ning sẽn rɩlgd maam la A yũnugd maamã."
  26,80,"Naab ninga, tɩ mam sã n wa ka keeme, A kõta maam laafɩ,"
  26,81,"Naab ning sẽn reegd-a mam yõorã la A leb n vʋʋg maamã,"
  26,82,"Naab ning mam sẽn tar tʋlsem t'a yaaf mam tʋʋm-tuutsã, dĩinã (yaoodã) raare."
  26,83,"M Soabã Wẽnde, kõ maam bʋʋd minim la lagem maam ne nin-sõmã wã;"
  26,84,"La maan maam tɩ m tɑl yʋ-noogo yaoolem zãmaan rãmbẽ,"
  26,85,"La maan maam tɩ m yɩ neemã arzãnã fa-rɩkda,"
  26,86,"La yaaf mam saambã, ad a yɩɩme n yaa menemda."
  26,87,"La ra wa ning-m yãnd Yikr raarã ye."
  26,88,"Raar ning arzεk la koamb sẽn pa nafde."
  26,89,"Rẽnda ned ning sẽn wa Wẽnd nengẽ ne sũur sẽn yɩlge""."
  26,90,"Tɩ b na n kolg arzãnã n kõ Wẽnd-zoεtbã."
  26,91,"La Gεhɩɩm Bugum na n vẽneg a meng n wuk ne sẽn belg b mensã,"
  26,92,"Tɩ b nɑ n yeel-bɑ: ""yãmb sẽn da yɩ n tũud bũmb ningã wã bεε,"
  26,93,"zẽng sẽn pa Wẽndã? Rẽ yĩnga b tõe n sõnga yãmbã? Bɩ b tõe n sõnga b mense?"""
  26,94,"B na n lob-b lame n kalem taaba, bãmb ne sẽn belg b bãmbã,"
  26,95,"La a ɭblɩɩs poorẽ rãmbã fãa gilli."
  26,96,"La b na n yeele, tɩ bãmb be Bugmã pʋgẽ n takd taaba:"
  26,97,"""Ne Wẽnde! Ad tõnd rag n bee meneng sẽn vẽneg pʋgẽ,"
  26,98,"tõnd sẽn wa n rɩkd yãmb n zemsd ne bõn-naandsã Soabã."
  26,99,"Bũmb pa menes tõnd n zʋʋg nin-wẽnsã ye."
  26,100,"La tõnd pa tar sugsd ye."
  26,101,"Zao tɩrg ka be me ye."
  26,102,"La tɩ lebgr sã n da beeme tɩ d paam n yɩ sɩd-kõtba."
  26,103,"Ad tagmas be woto (ɑ ɭbrɑɑhɩɩm kibɑrã lɑ yɑgsdbã bɑɑsgã) pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,104,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naaba n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,105,"A Nuuh nebã yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã,"
  26,106,"Wakat ning b saam-biig a Nuuh sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka zoet [Wẽnde]?''"
  26,107,"Ad mam yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm ne yãmba n yaa bas-m-yam soɑbɑ."
  26,108,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y pʋg maam."
  26,109,"Mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, ad mam keoorã bee bõn-naandɩ wã Soabã nengẽ."
  26,110,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y pʋg maam"
  26,111,"La b yeele: ""rẽ yĩngã tõnd na sak n kõ foom sɩda, tɩ yaool n yaa nin-yaalsã la sẽn pʋgd foomã?"""
  26,112,"La a yeele: ""mam ka tar bãngr ne b sẽn da tʋmd ye."
  26,113,"Ad b geelgã roga ne mam Soabã zug tɩ y sã n miẽ."
  26,114,"Mam ka na n rig sɩd-kɩtbã ye."
  26,115,"Mam ka zẽngã rẽnda bugsd sẽn vẽnege""."
  26,116,"La b yeele: ""yaa a Nuuhu, la tɩ fo sã n ka maan gũusgu, ad b na n loba foom [ne kuga]!"""
  26,117,"La a yeele: ""yaa m Soaba, ad mam nebã yagsa maam."
  26,118,"Bɩ F bʋ maam ne b sʋka, bʋʋd sẽn sãɑmd-b tɩ yaa vẽenega , la F tɩlg-ma la neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd n lagem maamã""."
  26,119,"Tɩ Tõnd na n tɩlg-a la neb nins sẽn kẽ n naag-a wã kogl pitgã pʋgẽ."
  26,120,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ Tõnd bõr neb a taabã (kɩfr-rãmbã)."
  26,121,"Ad tagmas be woto pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,122,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,123,"Ad a ʿAad rãmb yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã,"
  26,124,"Wakat ning b saam-biig a Huud sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka zoet [Wẽnde]?"
  26,125,"Ad mam yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm n yaa bas-m-yam ne yãmba."
  26,126,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y pʋg maam."
  26,127,"Mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, ad mam keoorã bee bõn-naandɩ wã Soabã nengẽ."
  26,128,"Rẽ yĩngã yãmb na n meta kunkubr zug fãa me-zãntg n reemdẽ bala?"
  26,129,"La y met ro-bεda (gãsdo) tɩ yaa wala yãmb na n duumame?"
  26,130,"La yãmb sã n na n maan n role, y maandame tɩ y yaa maan-n-zʋʋg rãmbã, tɩ ninbãan-zoeg ka be ye."
  26,131,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y pʋg maam."
  26,132,"Yaees-y Naab ning sẽn kõ yãmb bõn-sõmã wɑlɑ y sẽn mi wã."
  26,133,"Sẽn kõ yãmb rũms la koamba."
  26,134,"La pʋt la ko-soaya."
  26,135,"Ad mam yaeesda yãmb zugu, ra-kãseng raarã naongã."
  26,136,"La b yeele: ""zem tɩ fo maana tõnd waazʋ maa fo ka maane, fãa yaa a yembr tõnd nengẽ''."
  26,137,"Ad wãnde yaa rãeenem rãmb zʋgdo lɑ b rog-n-miki."
  26,138,"La b pa na n sɩbg tõnd ye."
  26,139,"Tɩ b yags-a, tɩ Tõnd halk-ba, ad tagmas be woto pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,140,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,141,"Ad a Ṯamuud rãmb yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã."
  26,142,"Wakat ning b saam-biig a Ṣaalɩḥ sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka zoet [Wẽnde]?''"
  26,143,"Ad mam yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm n yaa bas-m-yam ne yãmba.''"
  26,144,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnd la y pʋg maam."
  26,145,"Mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, ad mam keoorã bee bõn-naandɩ wã Soabã nengẽ."
  26,146,"Rẽ yĩnga, yãmb tẽedɑme tɩ b na basɑ yãmb kaanẽ tɩ yãmb be bas-m-yam pʋg bɑla?"
  26,147,"Tɩ y be pʋt pʋg la ko-sood pʋga"
  26,148,"La koodo la tamar tɩɩs biis sẽn yaa lom-lome (n sakd rɩɩbo)?"
  26,149,"La y peesd tãmsã n met rot tɩ yãmb yɑɑ sẽn tõe tʋʋmdã tɩ looge?"
  26,150,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnde la y pʋg maam."
  26,151,"La y ra wa tũ zʋʋg-toadg rãmbã sagell ye."
  26,152,"Neb nins sẽn kẽnd tẽngã zug ne sãoongã la b pa manegdã."
  26,153,"La b yeele: ""ad b maana foom tɩɩm,"
  26,154,"Fo ka baa fʋɩ n zʋʋg ned wala tõnd ye, bɩ f wa ne tagmas tɩ sã n mikame tɩ f naaga nin-sõma wã""."
  26,155,"La a yeele: ""woto yaa yʋgemde: a tara yũub raare, tɩ yãmb me tar yũub raar sẽn yãk n miẽ''."
  26,156,"Ra sɩɩs-y-yã-a ne wẽng ye, tɩ ra-wagell raarã sɩbgr wa yõk yãmb ye""."
  26,157,"La b kõs-a [n kʋ] tɩ b vẽeg beoog ne nimsa!"
  26,158,"Tɩ naongã yõk-ba, ad tagmas be woto pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,159,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,160,"Ad a Lʋʋṭ nebã yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã."
  26,161,"Wakat ning b saam-biig a Lʋʋṭ sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka nɑ n zoe [Wẽnde]?"
  26,162,"Ad mam yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm n yaa bas-m-yam ne yãmba."
  26,163,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnde la y pʋg maam."
  26,164,"Mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, ad mam keoorã bee bõn-naandɩ wã Soabã nengẽ."
  26,165,"Yãmb nɑ n baooda raop bõn-nɑɑndi wã sʋkɑ?"""
  26,166,"N yaool n basd pagbã yãmb Soabã sẽn naan n kõ yãmb tɩ yaa halaalã? Ad yãmb yaa zʋʋg-toadg rãmbã""."
  26,167,"La b yeele: ""yaa foo Lʋʋṭe! ad fo sã n ka tek n base, b na n rig-f lame n yi tẽngã""."
  26,168,"La a yeele: ""ad mam kisga yãmb tʋʋmdã,"
  26,169,"M Soaba, tɩlg maam la m zakã rãmbã n yi bãmbã sẽn tʋmdã""."
  26,170,"Tɩ Tõnd na n tɩlg-a la a zakã rãmb fãa gilli."
  26,171,"Rẽnda pʋg-yãanga, n naag halkdbã pʋgẽ."
  26,172,"Rẽ loogr poorẽ tɩ Tõnd na n halk sẽn ket-bã."
  26,173,"La Tõnd na n sik sa-koom b zugu, ɑd bugs-n-kong rãmb saag yɩ wẽnga."
  26,174,"Ad tagmas be woto pʋga la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,175,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,176,"Ad a Ayka nebã (kãgrẽ rãmbã) yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã."
  26,177,"Wakat ning a Sʋ'ʿayb sẽn wa n yeel-ba: ""rẽ yĩnga yãmb ka nɑ n zoe [Wẽnde]?''"
  26,178,"Ad mam yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm n yaa bas-m-yam ne yãmba."
  26,179,"Bɩ y zoe Wẽnde la y pʋg maam."
  26,180,"Mam pa kot yãmb keoor a zug ye, ad mam keoorã bee bõn-naandɩ wã Soabã nengẽ."
  26,181,"Pids-y vugbã la y ra yɩ neb nins sẽn boogd vugb ye."
  26,182,"La y pees ne pεεsdg sẽn tẽeg tɩrga."
  26,183,"Ra wa boog-y nebã teedã vugbã pʋgẽ ye, la y ra kẽn tẽn-gãngã zug ne sãang ye."
  26,184,"Zoe-y Naab ning sẽn naan-a yãmb la zãma-rãmb nins sẽn reng yãmb taoorã."
  26,185,"La b yeele: ""ad b maana foom tɩɩm,"
  26,186,"Fo ka baa fʋɩ n zʋʋg ned wala tõnd ye, la ad tõnd tẽedame tɩ fo yaa zĩri-be-neda."
  26,187,"Bɩ f kɩt tɩ bõn-wεdg yi saagẽ wã n lʋɩ tõnd zugu, tɩ sã n mikame tɩ fo yaa sɩd-soaba!"""
  26,188,"La a yeele: ""mam Soabã n mi bũmb ning yãmb sẽn maandã""."
  26,189,"Tɩ b na n yags-a, tɩ sawadg (maasem) raar sɩbgr na n gãd-ba, la ad raarã yɩɩ ra-kãseng raar naongo."
  26,190,"Ad tagmas be woto pʋga, la ad bãmbã sẽn waoog fãa pa sɩd-kõtb ye."
  26,191,"La ad fo Soabã yaa wilb Naab n yaa Yolsg Naaba."
  26,192,"Ad a sigame n yi bõn-naandsã Soab nengẽ."
  26,193,"Bas-m-yam yõ-yɩlemdã (Gibriil) n sik-a."
  26,194,"Fo sũurẽ wã, sẽn na yɩl tɩ fo yɩ bugsda."
  26,195,"Ne Laarab-rãmb zɩlemd sẽn vẽnege."
  26,196,"Ad a bee rãeenem (Tẽn-tʋʋmbã) gaf-rãmb pʋgẽ."
  26,197,"Rẽ yĩnga a ka yɩ yel-solemd ne bãmbã t'a ɭsraεεl bãngdbã wa tar a kɩbare?"
  26,198,"La tɩ b sã n da sik-a n kõ neb zẽms sẽn pa Laarab-rãmba."
  26,199,"Tɩ b wa karem-a n wĩnig-ba, b ra ka na n kõ sɩdɑ tɩ bɑla b pɑ fɑsmd-ɑ ye."
  26,200,"Yaa woto la Tõnd kẽes (Tẽn-tʋʋmbã yagsgo) nin-wẽnsã sũyẽ,"
  26,201,"B pa na n kõ (Alkʋrãanã) sɩda, hal tɩ b wa tʋg n yã naon-zabdgã,"
  26,202,"Naongã na n waa b nengẽ ne lingri, tɩ b pa tẽed ye."
  26,203,"La b yetdẽ: ""rẽ yĩnga, b na n kolla tõnd (tɩ d tuub bɩ)?"""
  26,204,"Rẽ yĩnga yaa Tõnd nongã la b yãgd n baoodẽ?"
  26,205,"Fo yãame tɩ Tõnd sã n wʋms-b noog yʋʋm saare,"
  26,206,"Rẽ poorẽ tɩ (nong) ning b sẽn da pʋlem-bã yaool n wa,"
  26,207,"Bõe lɑ bũmb ning b sẽn da wʋmd noogã na n tõog n nɑf-bɑ?."
  26,208,"Lɑ Tõnd pa halkd tẽnga, rẽndame tɩ D reng n tʋms Tẽn-tʋʋm tɩ tʋg n bugs-ba."
  26,209,"Tɩ yaa tẽegre, la Tõnd pa yɩ n yaa wẽgdb ye."
  26,210,"Ad pa Sʋɩtãamb n sig ne Alkʋrãɑnɑ ye."
  26,211,"A ra pa sõmb ne-ba, b pʋs n pa tõe."
  26,212,"Ad b lill-b lame tɩ b pa tõe n paam n kelg (Wẽnd goamã) ye."
  26,213,"Bɩ f ra wa bool soab zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, tɩ fo wa yɩ neb nins b sẽn na n namsã pʋgẽ ye."
  26,214,"La bugs fo rog-pẽtbã."
  26,215,"La gãneg f faagr pɩgs ne neb nins sẽn pʋgd foomã sẽn yaa sɩd-kõatbã."
  26,216,"La b sã n kɩɩs foom, bɩ f yeele: ""mam pigd n yii bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tʋmdã''."
  26,217,"La bobl f meng ne wilb Naabã la Yolsg Naabã."
  26,218,"Naab ning sẽn ne foomã, wakat ning fo sẽn wat n yik n deed pʋʋgã."
  26,219,"La fo sẽn wat n leebd suguud maandbã sʋka."
  26,220,"Ad A yaa Wʋmd n yaa Mita."
  26,221,"Rẽ yĩnga, m pɑ na n kõ-y kibar ne Sʋɩtãambã sẽn sigd neb nins nengẽ wã?"
  26,222,"B sigda zĩrimbeed soab sẽn yaa zunuub-bεd soab nengẽ."
  26,223,"B modgdame n na n pɑɑm n kelg sɑɑsẽ wã…la b wʋsg fãa yaa zĩrimbe-neba."
  26,224,"La yɩɩn-yɩɩndbã, yaa kεdgdbã n pʋgd-ba."
  26,225,"Rẽ yĩnga fo pa yãnd tɩ ko-soog (wεεng fãɑ) fãa pʋgẽ, bãmb n be beenẽ n faooda,"
  26,226,"La b yet bũmb ning b sẽn pa tʋmde?"
  26,227,"Rẽndɑ yɩɩn-yɩɩdb nins sẽn kõ sɩdã la b maan tʋʋm sõmã la b tẽegd Wẽnd yʋʋrã wʋsgã, la b wili, b sẽn wẽg-b loogr poorẽ. La wẽgdbã na wa n bãng lebgr zĩig ninga b sẽn na n wa lebã."
